title: TonysCheetahs
description:
MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS: Dual core AMD or Intel CPU with Virutalization support
3Gb RAM
Windows 7

Features auto resource collect, auto rank down (for farming), 6 hours extra shield with attack.

Open TonysCheetahs folder in program files.

Install "Andy" android emulator, download CoC from playstore (bottom right icon) register using the same email you use on your mobile.

Enter the co ordinates of your resources, enter 0 if N/A. Enter Co ordinates of buttons and troop rows, current are displayed (additional co-ordinate inputs are available if needed.)
Find co ordinates using mofiki, space bar gets the co ordinates.

To edit your co ordinates, enter 1000 or more in number of rank down attacks.

Start CoC fullscreen, enter wait time (0 for none), run period and number of rank down attacks,
CoC will disconnect if a wait time is set, the rest is automatic.

When attacking on your mobile you need to deploy all troops within 5 minutes when the app will interrupt (the battle will be completed with the deployed troops if interrupted). When you want to disconnect, wait for the app to interrupt then turn off your phone, don't exit CoC.

(It is advisable to restart your computer every 12-24 hours to stop "andy" from freezing.)
